{"tid":2045621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 香港今日既富貴，其實真係美國俾佢","createTime":"2020-06-01T02:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:57:54.000Z","uid":333163,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"372a6758021324e618d8f2ca53dcd73ab934abed","tid":2045621,"uid":333163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"香港最賺錢既金融業，其實只係美國認證香港係低風險地區，令資金聚集响香港，香港人再將資金打返大陸養活一炸大陸企業，所以成個過程都係好 low tech，香港只係一個大型找換店既老板仔，靠資金流出流入過河濕腳。做既野話難唔難，主要真係有呢個環境先做到，而唔係先有香港人。<br />\n<br />\n所以一旦美國唔再承認香港特殊地位，香港就再聚唔到資金養大陸，成個金融業就等死了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e16551b98539ed86789c37b3b03ae7f8140d5f9","tid":2045621,"uid":333163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"國家隊托市要用港紙，換港紙要先有美金，只要稍為用腦諗下就知，其實國家隊托市既子彈都係美國俾佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffe6130c13ac843d8bd6b3243a658b70c83ef6b","tid":2045621,"uid":333163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}